quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"M wẽen ne Mɑlεgs tedgdbã, rulg-rulgã."
  37,2,"La sẽn tãsd-b Sɑwɑtã tãsg tεkẽ n peegd-b n teesd Wẽnd sẽn tʋllẽ."
  37,3,"La sẽn karemd-b Tẽegrã sẽn yɑɑ Wẽnd goɑmã."
  37,4,"Ad yãmb Soabã, a yaa a Yembre."
  37,5,"Saas la tẽng la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋk Soaba, la Wĩndg pukr zĩis Naaba."
  37,6,"Ad Tond nagsa Dũni saagã ne faas-teed sẽn yaa ãdse."
  37,7,"La D leb n gũus-a n yi Sʋɩtãan fãa sẽn yaa tõta."
  37,8,"B pa tõe n kelg yĩngr rãmbã ye, b lobd-b-la wεεng fãa gilli."
  37,9,"Na zãag yĩnga, la b le tar nong sẽn ruumdi."
  37,10,"Rẽnda ned ning sẽn zaeeg-a zaeegr tɩ vɩleng sẽn wit pʋgl-a."
  37,11,"Bɩ f sok-b n gese, bãmb naanegã toolem n yɩɩd bɩ? Bɩ yaa bũmb ning Tõnd sẽn naanã? Ad Tõnd naan-b lame ne tãnd sẽn yaa tabende."
  37,12,"Pa woto ye, fo maanda yel-solemd tɩ bãmb yaandẽ."
  37,13,"La b sã n tẽeg-ba, b pa tẽegd ye."
  37,14,"La b sã n yã yel-solemde, la b sẽn boond taab n yaandẽ."
  37,15,"La b yeel yã: ""yãoã pa yɩ rẽnda tɩɩm sẽn vẽnege""."
  37,16,"B yeelame: ""rẽ yĩnga tõnd sã n ki n lebg tom la kõaba, b na leb n vʋʋg tõndo?"
  37,17,"La tõnd saam-rẽemsã fãa?"""
  37,18,"Yeele: ""n-ye"". Tɩ yãmb yaa b sẽn faag-b rãmba."
  37,19,"Ad a yaa tãs-vuk bal tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn gete."
  37,20,"Tɩ b yeele: ""yaa tõnd wɩɩbdo! Yãoondã yaa rolbã raare."
  37,21,"Yãoã yaa welgr raar ning yãmb sẽn da yɩ n yagsdẽ wã""."
  37,22,"Tigim-y b rãmb nins sẽn wẽgbã, b pagbã la bũmb nins b sẽn da yɩ n tũudẽ wã."
  37,23,"Zẽng tɩ pa Wẽndã, bɩ y kãag-y-b n tʋg Bugmã sorẽ."
  37,24,"La y yals-y-ba, tɩ b na n sok-b lame."
  37,25,"Yaa bõe n tar yãmb tɩ y pa sõngd taaba?."
  37,26,"Pa woto ye, bãmbã rũnda, b yaa sak-n-tũ rãmba."
  37,27,"Tɩ b sãnda togl sãnda n sogsd taaba."
  37,28,"N yetẽ: ""ad yãmb ra yɩɩme n wat tõnd nengẽ ne pãnga""."
  37,29,"Tɩ b yeele: ""yãmb pʋs n ra pa yɩ n yaa sɩd-kõtb ye""."
  37,30,"La tõnd ra pa tar ba pãng yãmb zug ye, yãmb pʋs n ra yɩɩ neb sẽn yaa kεdgdba."
  37,31,"Tõnd Soabã gomd sɩdga tõnd zugu, ad tõnd yaa (naongã) lεmbdba."
  37,32,"Tɩ tõnd kedg yãmba, ad tõnd yɩɩme n yaa kεdgdba."
  37,33,"La raar-n-kãngã, b fãa yaa lagem-n-taas naongã pʋga."
  37,34,"Ad tõnd yaa woto bal la D tʋm ne nin-wẽnsã."
  37,35,"Ad bãmb ra yɩɩme tɩ b sã n yeel-ba: ""soab kae sã n pa Wẽnde"". La b sẽn maand waoog-m-menga."
  37,36,"La b yetẽ: ""rẽ yĩnga tõnd yaa d soben-dãmbã basdba, yɩɩn-yɩɩnd sẽn yaa gãeeng yĩnga?""."
  37,37,"Pa woto dɛ! A waa ne sɩd la a sɩdg tẽn-tʋʋmbã."
  37,38,"Ad yãmb yaa naon-zabdgã lεmbdba."
  37,39,"La b pa rond yãmb rẽnda yãmb sẽn ra yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  37,40,"Ralla Wẽnd yembs nins b sẽn tɩlgã."
  37,41,"Bãmb rãmb n tar rɩtl b sẽn mi."
  37,42,"Sẽn ya tɩ-biisi, tɩ bãmb yaa b sẽn waoog-b rãmba."
  37,43,"Tɩ b be Neema arzãn-rãmbã pʋsẽ."
  37,44,"N be gãt zutu, n togl taaba."
  37,45,"Tɩ b gilgd b zut ne ko-tees sẽn yɑɑ yolgmd wɑ lɑ ko-nifri."
  37,46,"Pεεlg fudd n yaa noog ne a yũudba."
  37,47,"Suub kɑ ɑ pʋgẽ ye, ɑ pa zɑb b zutu."
  37,48,"La b tara pagb sẽn ya ges-koees rãmba, n ya pʋg-neeb nin sẽn yalme."
  37,49,"B yaa wala gεl sẽn gũusi."
  37,50,"Tɩ b sãnda togl sãnda n sogsd taaba."
  37,51,"Yεt n yeel b pʋgẽ wã : ""ad mam ra tara zao."
  37,52,"T'a ra yetẽ: ""rẽ yĩnga fo lagma sɩd kõtbã bɩ?''."
  37,53,"Tõnd sã n ki n lebg tom la kõaba rẽ yĩnga tõnd yaa b sẽn na n rol-b rãmb bɩ?"""
  37,54,"Tɩ sɩd-kõtã yeel tũud-n-tɑɑsã sẽn be Arzẽnɑ: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb pɑ na n wa tɩ d lik n ges ɑ sẽn mɑɑnegɑ?"""
  37,55,"T'a lɩk n yã-a Bugmã sʋka."
  37,56,"T'a yeele: ""m wẽen ne Wẽnde, fo ra na n halkẽ-la maam,"
  37,57,"La sã n ka mam Soabã neema wã yĩngã, m ra na n zĩnda b sẽn wa ne-b rãmb bugmẽ wã."
  37,58,"M mi tɩ tõnd ɑ Arzẽn koɑmb pa kiidb lɑ?."
  37,59,"Rẽnda d kũ-rãeengã? Tõnd pa b sẽn na n nams-b rãmb me ye?."
  37,60,"Ad woto la pʋɩ-bedre."
  37,61,"Bɩ tʋm-tʋmdbã tʋme, woto bilgr paang yĩnga."
  37,62,"Señ togs tɩ loogã, yẽ la sigb zĩig sõama sẽn yɩɩd bɩ yaa zakʋʋm tɩɩgã (tʋk sẽnego) ?."
  37,63,"Tõnd naan-a lame t'a yaa zarbg-n-gεsg ne wẽgdbã."
  37,64,"Ad a yaa tɩɩg sẽn yit Bugmã yẽgrẽ."
  37,65,"A bĩisã yaa wala Sʋɩtãams zutu."
  37,66,"La bãmb na n rɩ-a lame n pids-a b pʋsã."
  37,67,"Rẽ poorẽ b tara bõn-yũudi sẽn gẽdg ne ko-tʋʋlg n na n paas a zugu."
  37,68,"Rẽ poorẽ ad b lɛbeng zĩig yaa Bugmẽ wã."
  37,69,"Ad bãmb mika b saam-dãmbã tɩ b yaa menemdba."
  37,70,"Tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn zoet n wurd b vũunã tũub zugu."
  37,71,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka rãeenem-rãmbã wʋsg sẽn reng bãamb taoor menmame."
  37,72,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd tʋmsa bugsdb b pʋgẽ."
  37,73,"Bɩ f ges b sẽn bugs-b rãmbã baasg yɩɩ wãn-wãna?"
  37,74,"Ralla Wẽnd yembs nins b sẽn tɩlgã, (bãmb nɑ n põsɑ nɑngã)."
  37,75,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka a Nuuh boola Tõnd, la sakdb sɑkr sẽn be neer n yɩɩd yaa Tõndo."
  37,76,"La D tɩlg-a-la ne a zakã rãmb n yi naon-bedrã."
  37,77,"La D maan a koambã tɩ bãmb la kεlldba."
  37,78,"La D bas tɩ b na n wa gomd a yell yaoolem rãmbẽ wã."
  37,79,"Tɩlgr be ne a Nuuh bõn-naandsã pʋga."
  37,80,"Ad yaa woto bal la Tõnd rond manegdbã."
  37,81,"Ad a yaa Tõnd yembs nins sẽn ya sɩd-kõtbã a yembre."
  37,82,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd na n bõr neb a taabã."
  37,83,"La a ɭbraahɩɩm yɩɩme n dɩk a sorã n yɑ-ɑ yãɑgɑ."
  37,84,"Wakat ning a sẽn wa a Soabã nengẽ ne sũur sẽn yɩlge."
  37,85,"Wakat ning a sẽn wa n yeel a saambã la a zãma wã: ""yaa bõe la yãmb sẽn tũudã?"""
  37,86,"Zĩri soben-dãmb zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnd la yãmb rata?"
  37,87,"La yãmb tẽeda wãn-wãn ne bõn-nãandsã Soabã, tɩ sã n sεgɑ ne lɑgm-n-tɑɑre?"
  37,88,"T'a nak n ges ãdsẽ wã."
  37,89,"N yeel-bɑ: ""ad mam yaa bãada""."
  37,90,"Tɩ b ball n yi-a n gũd b kuidsi n looge."
  37,91,"T'a zãoos n kẽng b soben-dãmbẽ wã, n yeel: ""yãmb pa rɩt laa?''."
  37,92,"Bõe n tar yãmb tɩ y pa gomda?"""
  37,93,"T'a loog n ta n pãbd-b ne rɩtgo."
  37,94,"Tɩ b togl n wat a nengẽ ne yãgbo."
  37,95,"T'a yeele: ""yãmb tũuda bũmb ning yãmb sẽn peesdã''"
  37,96,"Tɩ Wẽnd n yaool n naan yãmb ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tʋmdã?"
  37,97,"Lɑ b yeelyã: ""me-y wulg a yĩngɑ, n lobg-a bugmã pʋga""."
  37,98,"Tɩ b tʋls-a ne wẽnga tɩ Tõnd maan tɩ bãmb lɑ bõnɑ rãmba."
  37,99,"T'a yeele: ""ad mam yaa loogda n tʋg m Soabẽ nengẽ, A na n kãndga maaam''."
  37,100,"Foom m Soabã! Kõ maam bi-sõngo."
  37,101,"Tɩ Tõnd noog a sũuri ne bi-ribl (ɭmaa-ɩɩl) sẽn yaa sugr soaba."
  37,102,"Lɑ ɑ sẽn wa n bi, n ta sõng-ɑ sãɑmbã n tʋm wakatã, a (ɭbraahɩɩm) yeelame: ""m biig sõngo, ad mam yãta gõeem pʋgẽ n kodgd foom, bɩ f gese fo tagsg yaa wãn-wãna?"" T'a yeele: yaa m baaba sõngo, maan b sẽn sagend-fã tɩ Wẽnd sã n sake, f na n mika maam tɩ m lagma sugr rãmbẽ""."
  37,103,"B yiibã fãa sẽn wa n sak n reeg b zugẽ, t'a gãneg-a a yεgdgẽ wã."
  37,104,"Tɩ Tõnd boaal-a: ""yaa foom ɭbrahɩɩma!''"
  37,105,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka fo sɩdga zãmsdã"", yaa woto bal la Tõnd rond manegdbã."
  37,106,"Ad wãnda la zarb-n-gɛsg sẽn vẽnege."
  37,107,"La Tõnd tεdg-a lame ne bõn-koadgdg sẽn bedme."
  37,108,"La D bas tɩ b na n gomd a yell yaoolem rãmbẽ wã."
  37,109,"Tɩlgr be a ɭbraahɩɩm yĩnga."
  37,110,"Yaa woto bal la tõnd rond manegdbã."
  37,111,"Ad a yaa Tõnd yembs nins sẽn yaa sɩd-kõtbã a yembre."
  37,112,"La D noog a sũur ne a ɭshaaka t'a yaa nabiyaam n yi nin-sõmsẽ wã."
  37,113,"La D bark-a (ɭsmaa-ɩɩl) la a ɭshaaka. Be b yiibã koamb pʋsẽ, manegd la wẽg-m-meng soab sẽn vẽnege."
  37,114,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd maana neema a Musa ne a Harʋʋn zugu."
  37,115,"La D tɩlg b yiibã la b yiibã neb n yi naon-bedrã."
  37,116,"La D sõng-b tɩ b yɩ n yaa bãmb la windba."
  37,117,"La D kõ b yiibã gaf vẽenega."
  37,118,"La D kãndg b yiibã n tʋg so-tɩrga."
  37,119,"La D bas tɩ b na wa gomd b yiibã yʋ-noogo yaoolem rãmbẽ wã."
  37,120,"Tɩlgr be a Musa ne a Harʋʋn yĩnga."
  37,121,"Ad yaa woto bal la Tõnd rond manegdbã."
  37,122,"Ad b yiibã yii Tõnd yembs nins sẽn yaa sɩd-kõtbã pʋgẽ."
  37,123,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka a ɭlyaas bee tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋgẽ."
  37,124,"Wakat ning a sẽn wa n yeel a nebã: ""yãmb pa zoet Wẽnde?."
  37,125,"Yãmb tũuda a Baal (rʋbga) la y basd Naand sẽn yɩɩd a ne sõmblem,"
  37,126,"Sẽn yaa Wẽndã, yãmb Soabã la yãmb baab-rãeemsã Soabã?"
  37,127,"Tɩ b yags-a. Ad bãmba yaa b sẽn na n wa ne b rãmba."
  37,128,"Ralla Wẽnd yembs nins b sẽn tɩlgã."
  37,129,"La D bas tɩ b na n wa gomd a yʋ-noogo yaoolem rãmbẽ wã."
  37,130,"Tɩlgr be ne a ɭlyaasɩɩn yĩnga."
  37,131,"Ad yaa woto bal la Tõnd rond manegdbã."
  37,132,"Ad a yaa Tõnd yembs nins sẽn yaa sɩd-kõtbã a yembre."
  37,133,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka a Lʋʋt bee tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋga."
  37,134,"Wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n tɩlg-a ne a zakã rãmb gilli."
  37,135,"Ralla pʋg-yãang n pa halkrã pʋgẽ."
  37,136,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd na n halk sẽn ket-bã."
  37,137,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka yãmb pɩʋʋgd-b-la yibeoogo."
  37,138,"La yʋngo, yãmb pa tar yam la?"
  37,139,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka a Yuunus bee tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋga."
  37,140,"Wakat ning a sẽn wa n zoe n kẽng kogl pitgã pʋga."
  37,141,"Tɩ b maan poeere, t'a zĩnd b sẽn wil-b rãmbã pʋgẽ, (ti b lu-bɑ mõgrẽ wã)."
  37,142,"Tɩ zĩnfã vel-a, tɩ yẽ yaa b sẽn sãbs-a soaba."
  37,143,"La tɩ sã n pa a sẽn yɩ n lagem sẽn yɩlg-b Wẽnd yʋʋrã."
  37,144,"A naan n zĩndẽ a pʋgẽ wã n tãag b sẽn na n yik-b raarã."
  37,145,"Tɩ Tõnd lob-a weo-raoogẽ wã t'a yaa bãada."
  37,146,"La Tõnd buls tɩɩg a yĩnga, tɩɩg sẽn tão tẽnga."
  37,147,"La D tʋms-a neb tus-koabg nengẽ pʋs n yɩɩdɑ rẽ."
  37,148,"Tɩ b kõ sɩda, tɩ Tõnd wʋms-b noog n tʋg wakato."
  37,149,"Bɩ f sok-b n gese, fo Soabã n so kom-pugli wã tɩ bãmb n so kom-ribli wã?"
  37,150,"Bɩ Tõnd naana Malεgsã tɩ yaa pagba, tɩ bãmb yɩ kaset-rãmbã?"
  37,151,"Yaa sɩda, ad bãmbã, b zĩri wã yĩnga b yetame:"
  37,152,"""Wẽnd rogame"". La sɩd la hakɩɩka ad b yaa pʋ-yagdba."
  37,153,"Rẽ yĩnga kom-pigli la A tũus n bas kom-ribli?"
  37,154,"Yaa bõe n tar yãmb tɩ y bʋʋd woto?"
  37,155,"Yãmb pa tagsd la?"
  37,156,"Bɩ yãmb tara daliil sẽn yɑɑ vẽenega?."
  37,157,"Bɩ y wa ne y gafã, tɩ y sã n da n yɩɩme n yaa sɩd-rãmba."
  37,158,"La b maan rogem n ning Yẽnda ne Malεgsã sʋka. La sɩd la hakɩɩka malεgsã bãngame tɩ ad Wẽnd nɑ n wɑɑ ne lɑgm-n-tɑɑrɑ rãmba n geel-bɑ."
  37,159,"Yɩlgemd be ne Wẽnde n yi bũmb ning b sẽn bilgdã."
  37,160,"Rẽnda Wẽnd yembs nins b sẽn tɩlgã."
  37,161,"Ad yãmba, la bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tũudã."
  37,162,"Yãmb pa yɩ n tõe menemes ned n yi sɩdɑ sor ye,"
  37,163,"Ralla ned ning sẽn yaa Bugmã kẽeda."
  37,164,"La malεk ba a ye pa be tõnd sʋka rẽndame t'a tara yalsg zĩig b sẽn mi."
  37,165,"La sɩd la haɩɩka Tõnd la tεdgdba, (Wẽnd tũubɑ pʋgẽ)."
  37,166,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd la yɩlgdba."
  37,167,"La b ra yɩɩme n yetẽ:"
  37,168,"""Tõnd sã n da tarẽ-la tẽegr sẽn yi rẽenem rãmbẽ wã."
  37,169,"D rag n na yɩ Wẽnd yembs nins b sẽn tɩlg-ba""."
  37,170,"Tɩ b kɩfl ne-a, la b na wa n bãnge."
  37,171,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd gomd rag n reng a taoore, Tõnd yembs nins sẽn ya-b tẽn-tʋʋmbã yĩnga."
  37,172,"Tɩ ad yaa bãmb n na n paam sõngrã."
  37,173,"La ad Tõnd tãp-biisã (sodaasã) bãmb la windbã."
  37,174,"Bɩ f ball n yi-ba n tʋg n tãag wakato."
  37,175,"La f koll-b tɩ b na wa n yã."
  37,176,"Paa Tõnd naongã la b yãgd n baoodẽ lɑ?"
  37,177,"La a sã n wa sig b samandẽ wã, b sẽn bugs-b rãmb yibeoog yɩ wẽnga."
  37,178,"Bɩ f ball n yi-b n tʋg n tãag wakato."
  37,179,"La f koall-b tɩ b na wa n yã."
  37,180,"Fo Soabã yɩlgame, sẽn yaa zɩslem Soabã n yi bũmb ninga b sẽn bilgdã."
  37,181,"La tɩlgr be ne tẽn-tʋʋmbã."
  37,182,"La pẽgr be ne Wẽnd sẽn yaa bõn-naandsã Soabã."
